GlassWave LLC App Privacy Policy
GlassWave LLC
built its apps and services as free applications that are advertising supported. Our Apps and Services are provided by GlassWave LLC at no cost and is intended for use as is.
							 We are committed to collecting only the information that is essential for delivering a reliable and enhanced experience. By minimizing data collection to only what is necessary, we strive to provide a safe environment while offering personalized, high-quality services that meet your needs without compromising your privacy.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and
				                    disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our Service.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation
				                    to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing and improving the
				                    Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described
				                    in this Privacy Policy.
The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, which is accessible
				                    at glasswave.co unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.
Information Collection and Use
For a better experience, while using our Service, we may require you to provide us with certain
				                    personally identifiable information, including but not limited to IP Address, Anonymized Device Analytics and basic device information such as screen size and model version.
				                    The information that we request will be retained by us and used as described in this privacy policy.
GlassWave also utilizes select third party services and partners to suppliment and enhance the quality of our applicatoins. You are encouraged to read and understand thier respective policies as well.
